{"tid":2331937,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"懲罰王宗堯 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-12-19T08:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T08:20:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"723c8043ee01b51282202bf6b9f9387c163164e6","tid":2331937,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201219/JJBTN7BWZJHSFDZFGIIQ3OWEJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201219%2FJJBTN7BWZJHSFDZFGIIQ3OWEJI%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=a2ad2109\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201219%2FJJBTN7BWZJHSFDZFGIIQ3OWEJI%2F&h=b12f7b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201219/JJBTN7BWZJHSFDZFGIIQ3OWEJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n懲罰王宗堯 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5tbKUSoSSSTPr_6qEI9t75A9UhY=/1280x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GJ7J4PFSGZGK5DJILBLAI4QCOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5tbKUSoSSSTPr_6qEI9t75A9UhY%3D%2F1280x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGJ7J4PFSGZGK5DJILBLAI4QCOY.jpg&h=f5094ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾天王宗堯在fb出了個帖文，談及他被告暴動，需要應付龐大的律師費。王宗堯因政治立場，過去兩年工作不多，雖多次為黃店宣傳，但有情有義的他很多時候只收取少許車馬費。律師費令他困擾。上網主動開口，要求黃店提供工作懲罰他。<br />\n<br />\n據悉王宗堯帖文一出，已經有黃店願意用正價請他工作。渣哥請他擔任一日代言人，出價10萬。珈啡公義亦都低調邀請他做代言人。《蘋果日報》為他開設了一個節目，叫《王探黃》，介紹全港好玩、好吃、好買、好打卡的地方，逢星期四晚10點半在「果燃台」同「蘋果動新聞YouTube Channel」播出。相信懲罰王宗堯的行動陸續有來，為他鬆一口氣的同時，<span class=\"orange\">也深深被香港人的團結及人情味感動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯形象正面，外形討好，演藝路上一路坎坷，全因其堅持自己的原則和立場，值得人敬佩。這也是他受黃店歡迎的原因。相信他的律師費應該可以順利解決。<br />\n<br />\n由此也對港共政府的卑鄙行徑深惡痛絕，他們為了阻止香港人抗爭，無所不用其極，隨隨便便告一個和平示威者暴動罪，官司纏身的同時，為律師費費盡思量，任何一個普通收入的人，都難以承受身心與經濟的多方煎熬。的確是會嚇退大多數人。但是，<span class=\"orange\">卻也令人更加認清港共政府的本質，心底只會更添反感</span>。<br />\n<br />\n希望所有被流氓政府濫捕濫告的手足都平安、順利。"},{"pid":"b50a1cd270ca8db948afb1a1ab4ff61186dc73d6","tid":2331937,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"以前佢寫am730  真係直到上年之前都估唔到佢係黃"},{"pid":"d442cdb2054269a09775b614590641408b3b7d27","tid":2331937,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"也深深被香港人的團結及人情味感動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9da5b595c480a884c31e96b348acff066969e00","tid":2331937,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"熱狗：偽黃偽人食人血饅頭，黃屍豬追星當抗爭，對唔對得住被捕手足"},{"pid":"d14ccfbe7da879fb5d58e62f7aba91479e288aa6","tid":2331937,"uid":50588,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"黃係黃<br />\n但講到形象正面，外形討好<br />\n咪又係狗公一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d442cdb2054269a09775b614590641408b3b7d27","tid":2331937,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"也深深被香港人的團結及人情味感動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}